x4freetext: THE SCATTERING OF 2.9 MEV NEUTRONS BY EVEN-EVEN
TIME OF FLIGHT METHOD WITH THE TIME RESOLUTION
CROSS SECTIONS ARE MEASURED RELATIVE TO
THE N-P SCATTERING C-S. TAKEN FROM FAST NEUTRON PHYS.,
DATA ARE COMPARED WITH OPTICAL MODEL AND HAUSER-FESHB.
CORRECTIONS ARE INTRODUCED ON THE MULTIPLE SCATTERING,
FLUX ABSORPTION IN THE SAMPLE AND ANGULAR RESOLUTION
